54 bool TShapeParamsGuiCompBase<Ui, Shape, ShapeModel>::OnAttached(imod::IModel* modelPtr)
55 {
56  if (BaseClass::OnAttached(modelPtr)){
57  const ShapesMap& shapesMap = BaseClass::GetShapesMap();
58  for ( typename ShapesMap::const_iterator iter = shapesMap.begin();
59  iter != shapesMap.end();
60  ++iter){

65  if (shapePtr != NULL){
